snippet.title: Rusty Barrel - A short horror game in which you pilot a small, cramped old submarine!
snippet.description:
Download for free on itch.io https://kenforest.itch.io/rusty-barrel?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt Rusty barrel is a short horror game in which you pilot a small, cramped and old submarine. You have to move through narrow openings in gorges on the ocean floor.
